{"tid":2281042,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Biden疫情顧問：啲疫苗應該喺美國人個個打哂之前 就向全世界供應","createTime":"2020-11-11T03:08:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-11T03:55:58.000Z","uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"1801c9edf3b6b6cc51676eca38eac763b46ca4fb","tid":2281042,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T03:08:38.000Z","msg":"Biden coronavirus adviser wants US to distribute vaccine globally before it's available to all Americans<br />\n<br />\nOncologist Dr. Zeke Emanuel, one of 10 advisory board members named to Democratic President-elect Joe Biden's coronavirus task force, has pushed the U.S. and other countries to not hoard a coronavirus vaccine.<br />\n<br />\nEmanuel, who served as a key architect of the Affordable Care Act under the Obama administration, co-authored a paper in September in which he encouraged officials to follow the &quot;Fair Priority Model,&quot; which calls for a &quot;fair international distribution of vaccine,&quot; rather than what he and his co-authors characterized as &quot;vaccine nationalism.&quot;<br />\n<br />\nThe model allows the country that produces the vaccine to hold onto enough of a supply to reach a threshold for herd immunity (&quot;Rt below 1&quot;). Beyond that, the model supports distributing the vaccine internationally, which means giving away or selling doses of the vaccine before it's available to every citizen in that country, Emanuel explained to Scientific American.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.foxnews.com/politics/biden-coronavirus-adviser-emanuel-vaccine-distribution\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fbiden-coronavirus-adviser-emanuel-vaccine-distribution&d=yH4nd0T6GS6ufvAy6eHVEceYC5A6rl8%2B6t9FBevN87M%3D&h=5f8718cd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.foxnews.com%2Fpolitics%2Fbiden-coronavirus-adviser-emanuel-vaccine-distribution&h=61fbec6f\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.foxnews.com/politics/biden-coronavirus-adviser-emanuel-vaccine-distribution</a>"},{"pid":"8873a61560be62ec06a27ec2bf698a36b6eb8ba6","tid":2281042,"uid":370061,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T03:09:37.000Z","msg":"美奸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d628c12b901ff26ebeb587b2cb64ad6079c01a7a","tid":2281042,"uid":259777,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T03:12:02.000Z","msg":"就係有呢啲美奸香港先會有輝瑞疫苗打<br />\n如果美國人打晒先既話，我諗到2022年香港都未有得分<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d310b18cf44375083991865dce6148e7550af24","tid":2281042,"uid":54125,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T03:13:46.000Z","msg":"出盡全力賣美國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b06a86438299ca56f25366eb33f4a7ac262f5b01","tid":2281042,"uid":248290,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T03:24:15.000Z","msg":"呢d 賣國賊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46aa11ddf66f2fe2fe8201a763b6054f8c412df2","tid":2281042,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T03:26:12.000Z","msg":"港共政府會唔會幫香港市民買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a7457d8caf52e1b77c7658fc6a993d3ad261c9c","tid":2281042,"uid":21545,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T03:29:38.000Z","msg":"Democrats my US<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eec6ec2eca28445e3092f9ff590dac9eceaac03","tid":2281042,"uid":122083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"46aa11ddf66f2fe2fe8201a763b6054f8c412df2","tid":2281042,"uid":377617,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T03:26:12.000Z","msg":"港共政府會唔會幫香港市民買<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-11T03:30:47.000Z","msg":"買黎自己打<br />\n香港市民